    "attributes": {
        "action": "Move Tax Bands in line with minimum wage increases",
        "additional_details": "Increase all tax bands by 28.5% in line with minimum wage increases.\r\nI.e. move starting band from \u00a312,570 to \u00a316,155 for 20% tax to start.\r\nMove the 40% band from \u00a350,270 to \u00a364,610\r\nMove the additional band from \u00a3125,140 to \u00a3160,838.\r\n",
        "background": "Review and change tax bands in line with minimum wage increases. Since freezing the bands, minimum wage has increased by 28.5%. The tax bands should have moved by same amount or minimum wage should not have increased.",
